   - Key code at line 319-327: `kafka_producer_->produce()`

2. **`src/ingestion/ingestion_service.cpp`** (Lines 92-230)
   - Consumes from Kafka topic via `RdKafka::KafkaConsumer`
   - Uses **TBB task_arena** for scalability (line 95: `arena_{tbb::task_arena::automatic}`)
   - Processes messages inside TBB arena (line 182-184)
   - Publishes validated events to internal `EventBus`

3. **`src/event_bus/event_bus_facade.cpp`** (Lines 126-475)
